        public boolean acceptablePosition(Molecule mol,

        Method to validate if a desired molecule position is valid. The position will be valid if there aren't any other molecules nearby.
        Parameters:
        mol - the molecule
        mapX - the molecules map ordered by the X coordinate
        isProblematic - flag indicating if the molecule is problematic, by example if the Desired location is between two thread submaps
